{"tid":248893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元稱7.22起不再評論內地香港時事　指與兒子有關","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T03:12:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbcb12a4b990bc11a7c01cf5ff2544e8e78ca4d","tid":248893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"經常發表評論的時事評論員、網上媒體「謎米香港」創辦人之一蕭若元，昨日在其網台節目宣布，7月22日起不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元在節目《最新蕭析》表示，由7月22日起，不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務，「呢兩個地方唔存在」，並指是由於其兒子蕭定一的要求。<br />\n<br />\n他說，作為時事評論員20年，「要講嘅嘢都講晒，再講都係重複」，而節目將改名為「退休蕭析」，內容以旅遊、「八卦」、哲學、人生及外國時事為主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00001/1495153052625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00001%2F1495153052625&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cfdc65b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00001%2F1495153052625&h=927a7849\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00001/1495153052625</a>"},{"pid":"a45dbffd95bffea0c725311be89058eb649aba40","tid":248893,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb83a805b26943a770a24dfc6d06b2af3df284f","tid":248893,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"阿一收左共產黨錢？"},{"pid":"b9192c0bd3e4e52079dc94cee829e9038a260b27","tid":248893,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"燒山終於肯收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse